                                                    ChemoCentryx to Hold First Quarter 2017 Financial Results Conference Call on Wednesday, May 10, 2017
                                                


                                                    GlobeNewswire – 
                                                    8:30 AM ET 04/27/2017
                                                


ChemoCentryx, Inc. (CCXI), today announced that the Company's first quarter 2017 financial results will be released after market close on Wednesday, May 10, 2017. To participate by telephone, please dial 303-8028 or 536-5167. About ChemoCentryxChemoCentryx (CCXI) is a biopharmaceutical company developing new medications targeted at inflammatory and autoimmune diseases, and cancer.

















                                                    ChemoCentryx Receives FDA Orphan Drug Designation for Avacopan in the Treatment of Debilitating Kidney Disease C3 Glomerulopathy (C3G)
                                                


                                                    GlobeNewswire – 
                                                    8:30 AM ET 03/22/2017
                                                


ChemoCentryx, Inc. (CCXI), a biopharmaceutical company developing new medications targeted at inflammatory and autoimmune diseases and cancer, announced today that the U.S. Food and Drug Administration has granted orphan drug designation for avacopan in the treatment of patients with C3 glomerulopathy.

















