                                                    8:30 AM ET 03/01/2017
                                                


ChemoCentryx, Inc. (CCXI), today announced that the Company's fourth quarter 2016 financial results will be released after market close on Tuesday, March 14, 2017. To participate by telephone, please dial 877-303-8028 or 760-536-5167. About ChemoCentryxChemoCentryx (CCXI) is a biopharmaceutical company developing new medications targeted at inflammatory and autoimmune diseases, and cancer.

















