ChemoCentryx, Inc. (CCXI), today announced that Thomas J. Schall, Ph.D., President and Chief Executive Officer, will present at the Cowen and Company 37th Annual Health Care Conference on Tuesday, March 7, 2017 at 10:00 a.m. ET.

















