-- ChemoCentryx (CCXI) retains all rights in the United States and China; Vifor Pharma gains additional marketing rights in Asia, including Japan and Middle Eastern markets -- -- ChemoCentryx (CCXI) to receive additional USD 20 million upfront cash commitment plus royalties on potential net sales --  -- ChemoCentryx (CCXI) remains responsible for worldwide development of avacopan -- MOUNTAIN VIEW, Calif., Feb. 14, ...












